    missionCriticalWorkflowFilter: "Prioritize bundle workflows that are mission-critical infrastructure, such as KYC, loan origination, legal review, accounting close, compliance checks, or customer operations where a miss can cost millions.",
    hackathonReliabilityGap: "Separate the bundle hackathon demo from production workflows: an 80% prototype is not the product; the drudgery is the edge-case work needed for the final 5% to 20% of consistency and 99% reliability.",
